race.description: Bunbury Cup On Sale Now Handicap
race.comment: Very good race but sticking with the honest IMAPAGETHREE GIRL (8). Placed 2/3 this time in, the latest running on hard to just miss in a similar race at Pinjarra last time. Drawn for a soft run and expected to be in the finish. HEZ GOT THE SAFE (3) is a super consistent type with one win but a host of minors from nine starts. Missed a nose last time at Pinjarra and goes well here. Should be in the finish. THE SCHOLAR (6) resumed from a break with a huge all the way win, scoring by five. That was in maiden grade but has good upside and can measure up again. MANGIFERA (9) is another who is skipping in grade. Was a dominant Class 1 winner last time but also has good upside and rates among the main chances. MAGICASH (10) has been thereabouts without winning and deserves to break through.
